Title: It Came from Hollywood
Actors: Dan Aykroyd, John Candy, Cheech Marin, Tommy Chong
Plot: Dan Ackroyd, John Candy, Gilda Radner and Cheech and Chong present this compilation of classic bad films from the 50's, 60's and 70's. Special features on gorilla pictures, anti-marijuana films and a special tribute to the worst film maker of all-time, Ed Wood.
